WEBVTT

00:00.117 --> 00:02.032
Why have I never noticed
this before?

00:02.035 --> 00:04.261
Is he not the very spit and
image of Uncle Ross?

00:04.263 --> 00:08.238
My child is due in December. I'd
prefer it to be born in November.

00:08.240 --> 00:10.238
I shall make up a medicine
to produce a living

00:10.240 --> 00:11.798
child in the manner you desire.

00:11.800 --> 00:13.798
I will have you expelled
from parliament!

00:13.800 --> 00:15.198
Will you, George?

00:15.200 --> 00:16.998
And how will you manage that?

00:17.000 --> 00:18.878
Promise me you won't
go after George.

00:18.880 --> 00:21.678
I couldn't bear to have the feud
stoked up again.

00:21.680 --> 00:25.198
Both of us have been afflicted
by the loss of our daughter.

00:25.200 --> 00:28.438
Our abiding love for each other
will mend what has been broken.

00:30.880 --> 00:32.158
You have a daughter.

00:32.159 --> 00:35.518
Do you not think there be more to
life than carnal love?

00:35.520 --> 00:39.678
Be my wife in name only,
I'll never ask you for more.

00:39.680 --> 00:42.758
Why is it so dark, George?
I'm afraid of the dark.

00:42.760 --> 00:44.040
Do not be afraid, my love.

00:45.240 --> 00:46.598
Elizabeth is dead.

00:46.600 --> 00:48.520
Go! See what we have brought her to!

00:50.680 --> 00:53.158
Why would I want any of this

00:53.160 --> 00:56.158
if she is not here to share
it with me?

00:56.160 --> 00:58.238
Elizabeth was your first love.

00:58.240 --> 01:00.078
But not my last.

01:00.080 --> 01:02.438
I made that choice long ago.

01:02.440 --> 01:03.480
And I.

